#: ../../B/blue-goo.rst:9
msgid ""
"Term for ‘police’ :ref:`nanobot`\\s intended to prevent :ref:`gray-goo`\\, "
"denature hazardous waste, destroy pollution, put ozone back into the "
"stratosphere, prevent halitosis, and promote truth, justice, and the "
"American way, etc. The term \"Blue Goo\" can be found in Dr. Seuss's *Fox In"
" Socks* to refer to a substance much like bubblegum. ‘Would you like to chew"
" blue goo, sir?’. See :ref:`nanotechnology`\\."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`gray-goo`\\ "
"を防ぎ、有害廃棄物を無毒化し、汚染を破壊し、オゾンを成層圏に戻し、口臭を防ぎ、真実・正義・アメリカ流を推進する、等々を意図した‘警察’\\ "
":ref:`nanobot`\\ を指す用語。「Blue Goo」という言葉は、Dr. Seussの\\ *Fox In Socks*\\ "
"に、風船ガムによく似た物質を指して見られる。「青いgooを噛んでみますか、お客さん?」。\\ :ref:`nanotechnology`\\ を参照。"
